 Real Faith CD music Product Description

Real Faith album for sale by Brian Free was released Feb 21, 2008 on the Daywind label. Personnel: Mike Payne, Kelly Back, Chuck Butler (guitar); The Nashville String Machine (strings); Gordon Mote (piano); Ricky Free (drums). Real Faith CD music contains a single disc with 10 songs. Audio Mixer: Barry Weeks. Photographer: Kimberly Lancaster Real Faith songs.


